http://purl.org/dc/terms/description.value: This course is a scientific approach to plant science using scientific principles and applied management practices. Emphasis is on genetics, scientific experimentation and reporting, and advanced plant science systems. Opportunities are provided for students to participate in supervised experience and FFA.
